Welcome to the Dollhouse;;86;;90;;R;;Middle-school student Dawn Weiner (Heather Matarazzo) faces degradation at school -- where she is teased constantly -- and at home. The middle child between nerdy older brother Mark (Matthew Faber) and perky younger sister Missy (Daria Kalinina), Dawn can't seem to find a place to belong. Although she has a crush on a cute boy (Eric Mabius) whom her brother knows, she can only catch the attention of bully Brandon (Brendan Sexton Jr.), who threatens her to show affection.;;Comedy,Drama;;Todd Solondz;;1995;;Heather Matarazzo,Daria Kalinina,Matthew Faber,Angela Pietropinto,Bill Buell,Brendan Sexton III,Eric Mabius,Rica Martens,Victoria Davis;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/welcome_to_the_dollhouse